\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
These are the names of ancesters of Yesu Keriso. Yesu was from Deifid's family. Deifid was Ebraam's family.
\par\pard\plain \s194\ql\fi-540\lin720\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
Ebraam was the father of Aisek,
\par\pard\plain \s195\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Aisek was the father of Jeikof,
\par\pard\plain \s194\ql\fi-540\lin720\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Jeikof was the father of Judas and his brothers,
\par\pard\plain \s195\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
Judas was the father of Feres and Jerai and their mother was Tamar,
\par\pard\plain \s195\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Feres was the father of Esron,
\par\pard\plain \s195\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Esron was the father of Ram,
\par\pard\plain \s195\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
Ram was the father of Aminadab,
\par\pard\plain \s195\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Aminadab was the father of Nason,
\par\pard\plain \s195\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Nason was the father of Salmon,
\par\pard\plain \s195\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
Salmon was the father of Boas, whose mother was Raaf,
\par\pard\plain \s195\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Boas was the father of Obed, whose mother was Rut,
