\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
But after he was thinking about this, from the man carrying heavenly message(angel) of the Lord appeared him in a dream and said, "Josef son of Deifid, do not be afraid to marry Meri as [your] wife. Because what is conceived in her is from the God Spirit. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
