"The unmarried woman without sleeping with man(virgin) will be pregnant and give birth to a son, and they will call a name Immanwel"{\super a{\footnote \pard\plain \s212\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28  {\super a}{{\cs214\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 1.23 }
{\cs215\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Aisaya 7:14}
}}}
(this meaning is 'God is with us').
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 24\~}
