But they.d didn't sleep together until Meri gave birth to a son. He gave him the name Yesu.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 2
