When you.p give to the needy people, don't do with wide sound like the people who are good outside but inside no, do in the meeting houses and on the road so that people honer them. I tell you.p the truth, they have already received their reward. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
But when you.p give to the poor people, do not let your.p left hand know what your.p right hand is doing, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
so that your.p giving thing must be in secret. Then your.p Father who sees what is done in secret will give a reward you.p.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Yesu taught about talking with God(prayer)
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
And when you.p talk with God, do not be like the hypocrites who love to stand in talking with God in the meeting houses and on the big street in order that people will see them. I tell you.p the truth, they have received their reward in full. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
But when you.p talk with God, go into your.p house, close the door and talk with God to him your.p(pl) Father, who is unseen. Then your.p Father who sees doing secretly will reward you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
When you.p talk with God, do not say many without.meaning talk like outside people(Gentiles) are, because they think their gods will hear for many talks. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
Do not be like they are, because your.p Father already knows what you.p need before you.p ask him. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
So, this is how you.p should talk with God:
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 'Our Father in heaven,
