\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
If you.p forget other people's sin when they have done to you.p, your.p Father in heaven will also forget your.p sin. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
