a man's enemies will come from within his own family.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 37\~}
"Anyone who loves his father or mother very much, but his love to me is small, he is not fit to follow me. Anyone who loves his son or daughter very much, but his love to me is small, he is not fit to follow me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 38\~}
Anyone who does not carry his cross and follow me, he is not fit to follow me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 39\~}
Anyone who try to gain his own life will lose it, and who loses his life for my sake will find it.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Whoever helps Yesu's group will receive a good reward
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 40\~}
