\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
After when Yesu had finished instructing talk to his 12 following men, he went from there to teach and preach to the towns of Galili region.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
When Jon heard in darkness house what Keriso was doing, he sent his following men {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
to ask him, "Are you.s the one who is coming, or should we wait someone else?\u8221?
