Yesu answered them, \u8220?Go back and report to Jon what you.p are hearing and seeing: {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
The blind can see, the lame start walking, those who suffer from bad skin diseases are made clean, the deaf hear, the dead are raised, and the good talk is in preaching to them the poor. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
