\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
While Jon's following men were leaving, Yesu began talking about Jon to the crowds: \u8220?Which man's face did you.p go out to see into the desert? A long grass which bows in the wind? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
