What did you.p go out to see? To which God's man who make know(prophet)? Yes, I tell you.p, Jon surpasses all other God's men who make know(prophets). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
This is the one about whom it is written in Scripture:
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 "I, God, will send my talk carrying man ahead of you.s
