Until the time of John all the prophets and the Law of Moses spoke about the heavenly kingdom. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
If you.p are willing to believe my talk, Jon is Elaija who was to come. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
They who has ears, should listen.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
\u8220?To what can I compare this generation? They are like children in the open/wide place calling other children:
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
\u8216?We played the flute for you.p,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 and you.p did not dance;
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 we sang funeral songs,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 but you.p did not cry!\u8217?
