At that time Yesu said, \u8220?I praise you.s, Father, Lord of heaven and earth, because you.s have hidden these things' meaning from these people who has wisdom and knowledge, but you.p have known and put clear to them ordinary people who are like little children. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 26\~}
Yes, Father, this was for how your will come true.
