\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
Saimon Fit\u232? answered him, \u8220?You.s are that Keriso, the Son of the living God.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
Yesu answered him, \u8220?Blessed are you.s, Saimon son of Jona! This truth did not come to you.s from people, but my Father gave to you from heaven. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
And I tell you.p that you.s are Fit\u232?, its meaning is the rock, on this I will build my family(church), and the power of death will not defeat it. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
I will give you.s the keys of the kingdom of heaven. Whatever you.s bind in this earth will also be bound in heaven, and in the same way whatever you.s loose in this earth will also be loosed in heaven.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
Then he stopped his following men not to tell anyone that he was that Keriso.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Yesu told them about his suffering and death
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
From that time on Yesu began to say to his following men, "I must go to Jerusalem and suffer in the hands of the head people, the leading(chief) sacrifice burning people(priests), and the teaching men of the law. They will kill me, but three days later God will raise me to life.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 22\~}
Fit\u232? took him aside and rebuked him. \u8220?No, Lord! God will never let this happen to you.s!\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 23\~}
Yesu turned and said to Fit\u232?, \u8220?S\u225?if\u232?r, get away from me! You.s are an obstacle to me, because your.s thoughts don't come from God. But you are thinking like how people think.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 24\~}
Then Yesu said to his following men, \u8220?Who starts following me he must forget himself, and carry his cross and follow me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 25\~}
Who wants to save his own earthly life will lose eternal life; but who loses his own earthly life for my sake he will get the eternal life. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 26\~}
A person could get the whole world for himself. But if he loses his eternal life, this will not be any good for him. There is nothing that a person can give to get back his life. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 27\~}
The Son of Man is about to come with his men carrying heavenly message(angels) in the big light(glory) of his Father, and he will reward each one according to their deeds. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 28\~}
I tell you.p the truth, some who are here will not die until they have seen the Son of Man come and he will be King.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 17
