As they were coming down the mountain, Yesu said them strongly, \u8220?Don\u700?t tell anyone what you.p have seen, until God raises back the Son of Man from the dead.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
