\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Yesu makes a boy good with a evil spirit
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
When they returned to the crowd, a man came to Yesu and knelt before him, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
and he said, \u8220?Lord, have mercy on my son! He is an epileptic and has big suffering. He often goes into the fire and he falls into water. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
