\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
Yesu answered him, \u8220?You.p truly without.approving evil generation! How long must I stay with you.p? How long will you give me burden? Bring the boy to me!\u8221? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
Yesu said to the evil spirit, "Come out!" it went out and at once the son was became good.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
Then his following men came to him only themselves and asked him, \u8220?Why we are not able to cast the evil spirit out?\u8221? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
Yesu answered them, \u8220?Because your.p big mind(faith) is very small. I tell you.p truth, if you.p have big mind(faith) like as a small seed, you.p say to this mountain, \u8216?Go from here to there!\u8217? and it will go. You can do whatever."{\super d{\footnote \pard\plain \s212\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28  {\super d}{{\cs214\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 17.21 }
