\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
Yesu called a little child to himself and put the child among them, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
and he said to them: \u8220?I tell you.p the truth, unless you.p change and become like children, you.p will never enter the kingdom of heaven. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
So, anyone who becomes lower as this little child is very big in the kingdom of heaven. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
