They came to a place named Golgota, its meaning is, \u8220?The place of the skull's shape.\u8221? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 34\~}
There they offered Yesu bitter alcohol, but after he tasted it, did not drink it.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 35\~}
