After that they sat there and watched him. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 37\~}
Above his head they put wood piece with this letter to make them what he did: "This is Yesu, the ruling man of the Ju people.\u8221? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 38\~}
Then they nailed two thiefs with Yesu, one on the right side and the other on the left side.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 39\~}
