\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
Suddenly Yesu met those two women and said, \u8220?Good morning.\u8221? They.d came up to him, and hold his feet, and worshiped him. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
Yesu said to them.d, \u8220?Do not be afraid. Go and tell my following men to go to Galili region, and there they will see me.\u8221?
