When they saw Yesu, all of them worshiped him, but some following men still were doubting. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
Yesu came close to them and said to them, \u8220?God gave me all authority in heaven and on earth. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
