So they left the crowds [behind], and his following men started. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 37\~}
The storm came up in the lake. The waves broke over the bout, [so that] it was nearly swamped.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 38\~}
Yesu was in bottom of the bout., sleeping. He slept like died(deeply). His following men woke him up and shouting, "Teacher, we are going to drown, don't you care us?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 39\~}
He got up, said to the wind and waves, "Be quiet." It was completely calm.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 40\~}
Yesu said to his following men, "Why are you afraid? Where is your big mind(faith)?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 41\~}
They were very afraid and said to each other, "Who is this? [Even] the wind and the waves obey him\u451?"
