One of Yesu's family(church) head man, name Jairus came there to see Yesu, he knelt down to his foot {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 23\~}
and he asked Yesu to help him. He said, "My daughter is very sick! Come and lay hands on her, she will be healed. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 24\~}
Yesu went with Jairus, Many people followed him and people were still gethering. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 25\~}
In the crowd woman was there who was bleeding for 12 years. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 26\~}
She always went to the doctors, and they didn't heal her, yet they were giving more pain. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 27\~}
When woman heard about Yesu, she came in beind Yesu in the crowd and toched his cloth, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 28\~}
woman thought, " When I tough his clothes, I will be healed." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 29\~}
When she touched him his cloth, her bleeding stopped and she felt in herself that I am healed.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 30\~}
At once the Power of Yesu left [from him]. He turned around to the people and asked, "Who touched my clothes?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 31\~}
His following men said to him, "Look those people who surrounded you! How did you ask, who touched you?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 32\~}
