The woman knew what had happened to her, and went frightenly to Yesu and knelt. She told him the whole the truth. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 34\~}
Yesu said to woman, "You are healed because of your big mind(faith). Go happily and you are helaed from your proplem."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 35\~}
