\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 36\~}
Yesu ignored their saying, Yesu told Jairus, "don't be afraid; trust me."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 37\~}
Yesu did not allow anyone to go with him only Fit\u232?, Jems a Jon small brother Jon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 38\~}
When they came to the house of Jairus, Yesu saw people worried and cried and made a noise {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 39\~}
So Yesu went in the house and said to them, "Why do you cry? the child is not dead but sleep." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 40\~}
But they laughed at him what he said.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Later Yesu told them, "All of you go out of the house," Yesu took the child's father and mother and his three following man where child was sleeping. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 41\~}
He hold the child on his hand and said to her, "Talita kum!"(its meaning, "Little girl, I say to you, wake up!") {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 42\~}
Not long the girl stood up and walked (Girl was 12 years old). They were surprised. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 43\~}
But Yesu gave stick orders not to say about this what has happened. So Yesu told to them, "Give the food!"
