the son of Jeikof, the son of Aisek,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 the son of Ebraam, the son of Tera, the son of Naor,
