\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 23\~}
Yesu said to them, "You will take this wise talk to me, 'Doctor, heal yourself\u451?' And you will tell me, 'Do here in your hometown what we have heard that you did in Kafernam."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 24\~}
He continued, "I will tell truth, all God's man who make know(prophet) don't be welcomed in his hometown. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 25\~}
