But Elaija was not sent to any of the Ju people, but to only a widow in Jarefat in Sidon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 27\~}
There were many in Israil with leprosy[with skin disease] in the time of Elisa, yet not one of them was cleasend [but] only Naaman from the Siria.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 28\~}
All the people in the meeting house were angry when they heard this talks. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 29\~}
