He cuts every branches in me which does not produce fruit, and he prunes which one produce fruit, so that they will be very fruitful. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
You are pruned because of the talk which I have spoken to you. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
Remain in me, and I will still be in you.p. No other brance will just produce fruit by itself unless it joins to the vine. In the same way you.p yourselves cannot produce fruit unless you.p are still in me.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
I am the vine, and you are branches. If a man still is in me and I am in him, he will produce many fruits; without me you cannot do anything. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
If you still are not in me, you are like branches that they throw them away and it becomes dry. People pick them up, throw them to the fire and burn. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
If you are still in me, and my talk still in you, ask whatever you.p want, and [God] will do it to you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
This is my Father's big light(glory) by that you produce many fruits, and you show yourselves are my followers.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
Just like Father loved me, and I loved you.p, you must continually stay in my love. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
If you obey my talk, you will still be in my love, just like I had obeyed Father's talk and I am still in his love. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
I have told you this in order that my joy will be with you.p and in order that your.p joy may be full.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
This is my commandment; love each other just like I have loved you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
Very high love to your friends is to give your life for them. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
You.p are my friends if you.p do what I said. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
I do not call you without.payment working men(servants) without pay, because the without.payment working men(servants) will not know about his owner's work, but I call you friends, because everything what I have known from the Father I have made you.p known. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
You.p did not choose me, but I chose you and appointed you in order that you will go to produce fruit, fruit which will exist. And for what you.p may ask in my name, the Father will give it to you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
This is my commandment: love one another.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 The world hates Yesu's followers
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
If the world hates you.p, you.p must remember that They had hated me first. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
If you were of the world, it will love you because you are its own. But you are not of the world, and I have chosen you from the world. In this reason world hates you. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
Remember the talk I had told you: 'The without.payment working man(servant) does not surpass his master. If they persecuted me, they will also persecute you in the same way. If they hear to my teaching, they will also hear to your teaching. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
They will persecute you in what way because of my name because they do not know who sent me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 22\~}
If I would not come and talk to them, they would not have been guilty of sin; But now they cannot say, we did not do wrong. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 23\~}
Who hates me also hates my Father in the same way. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 24\~}
If I had not done special workings(miracles) to them which no one did, they would not been guilty of sin. But in what way they have seen and they still hated me and my Father. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 25\~}
