\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 25\~}
I have spoken eampletalk, in order to explain to you.p what I had spoken, the day is coming here where I will not speak this example talk but I tell you clearly about my Father. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 26\~}
