\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 "Father, the time has come. Give big light(glory) to your Son in order that the Son will give you the big light(glory). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
