If your.s friend is distressed because of what you.s eat, you.s are no longer acting in love. Do not destroy by your.s eating food your.s friend for whom Keriso died. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
Therefore do not let what you.p know is good be spoken of as evil. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
The ruling of God is not a matter of eating and drinking, but of straight thing, peace and joy in the God Spirit, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
because anyone who serves Keriso in this way is pleasing to God and people approve of you too.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
Therefore we make every effort to do what leads us to peace and to help each other. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
Do not destroy the work of God for the sake of food. All foods are clean, but it is wrong for a person to eat anything that causes someone else to fall into sin. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
It is very good not to eat meat or drink alcohol or to do anything else that will cause your.s friend to fall. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 22\~}
Whatever you.s truly approve(believe) about these things keep between yourself and God. Blessed is the one who does not condemn himself by what he approves. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 23\~}
But whoever has two minds is condemned if he eats, because his eating food is not from big mind(faith), and everything that does not come from big mind(faith) is sin.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 15
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
We who are strong in big mind(faith) ought to help those truly approving men(believers) who are without.power and not to please ourselves. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
We should please our close people(neighbors) for their good, to build them up in the big mind(faith). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
Even Keriso did not please himself. As the scripture say, \u8220?The insults of those who insult you.p have fallen on me.\u8221? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
Everything that was written in the past was written to teach us. And the scripture give us hope and encouragement as we wait patiently for God's promises to be fufilled.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
May the God who gives endurance and encouragement give you.p a spirit of unity among yourselves when you.p follow Keriso Yesu, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
so that with one mind and one voice you.p may praise the God and Father of our Lord Yesu Keriso.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
Then accept one another, just as Keriso accepted you.p, in order to bring praise to God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
I tell you.p that Keriso has become a without.payment working man(servant) of the Israil people on behalf of God\u700?s truth, so that the without.lying talks(promises) made to the anscestors might be confirmed {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
and so that the Side people might praise God for his mercy. As the scripture says,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 \u8220?Therefore I will praise you.p among the Side people.
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 I will give the sing of praise of your.s name.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s61\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
Again, it says,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 \u8220?Rejoice, you.p Side people, with God's people.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s61\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
And again,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 \u8220?Praise the Lord, all you.p Side people.
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Praise him, all you people.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s61\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
And again, Aisaya says,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 \u8220?One man from Jesi's family will became with power,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 one who will arise to rule over all the nations;
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 the Side people will hope to him.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
May the God of hope fill you.p with all joy and peace because you.p trust in him, so that you.p may overflow with hope by the power of the God Spirit.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Fol the minister to the Side people
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
My friends, I myself know that you.p yourselves are full of goodness with all knowledge and you.p are able to teach each other all about them. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
I have written you.p quite boldly on some points, to make them know again, because of the grace God gave me {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
to be a minister of Keriso Yesu to the Side people like the burning sacrifice man(priest)'s duty of proclaiming the good talk of God, so that the Side people might become an offering acceptable to God. The God Spirit has made them holy.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
Therefore I am proud in Keriso Yesu in my service to God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
I will not boast to speak of anything but what Keriso did through me to lead the Side people to obey God by what I have said and done, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
by the power of surprising things(signs) and special things(wonders), through the power of the Spirit of God. So from Jerusalem all the way around to Illirikum, I have fully proclaimed the good talk of Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
My always wanting is to preach the good talk about Keriso where they did not hear about him, and where someone did not build on the Yesu's family(church). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
But, as it is sait in the scripture,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 \u8220?Those who were not told about him will see,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 and those who have not heard will understand.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Fol\u700?s Plan to Visit Rom
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 22\~}
That is why, many times, I have been hindered from coming to you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 23\~}
But now I have finished my work in these regions, and after I have waited this long years, I want to see you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 24\~}
So, I plan to go to Sfain. When I go, I will stop in Rom, and when I want to stay with you.p for a while, you.p will send me from there. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 25\~}
But before I come, I must go to Jerusalem to take offering things to the truly approving people(believers) there. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 26\~}
Makedonia people and Akaya people were pleased to make a contribution for the poor people who are the Lord\u700?s people in Jerusalem. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 27\~}
They were pleased to do that thing, That thing is very good, because it's like their repayment to Ju people. Because if the Side people received the spiritual blessings from Ju believers, so the Side people should reture to Ju people with their bodily blessings. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 28\~}
When I have delivered this money and completed this good deed of theirs, I will come to see you on my way to Sfein. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 29\~}
I know when I come to you.p, I will come with big blessing of Keriso to you.p.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 30\~}
Friends, I urge you.p by our Lord Yesu Keriso and by the love of the God Spirit, to join me in my fighting by talking with God(praying) for me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 31\~}
Talk with God that I may be saved from the people who do not truly approve(unbeliever) in Judia. Also talk with God that believers there are willing to accept this giving I am taking to Jerusalem. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 32\~}
Then, by the will of God, I will come to you.p with joy and I will rest with you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 33\~}
The God of peace be with you.p all. Amen.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 16
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Fol's greetings to his friends
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
I give to you.p our sister Fobe, who is worker in Yesu's family(church) which is in Kenkria. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
I ask you.p to receive Fobe in the Lord with very high respect among Keriso's people and to help her what help if she need from you.p, because she herself has been the big help to many people, and also helped me.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
Give greetings to Frisila and Akwila, my fellow workers in the Keriso Yesu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
They put their lives behalf to help me. I give thank talk to them, not only I, but all the outside man's Yesu's families(churches) as well. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
Give greetings also to the Yesu's family(church) that meet in their house.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Give greetings also to my loving friend Efanetus, who was the first believer to Kersio in the province of Esia to truly approve(believe) Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
Give greetings to Meri, who has worked so hard for you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
Give greetings also to Andronikus and Junias, my two relatives who were in darkness house with me. They are highly respected among the men with Yesu's authority(apostles), and they first came into Keriso I did after.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
Give greetings to \u193?mbliatus, whom I love in the Lord. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
Give greetings also to Urbanus, our co-worker in Keriso, and to my loving friend St\u225?kis. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
Give greetings to Afeles, a good man who is approved in Keriso. Give greetings to those who are in the family of Aristobulus. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
Give greetings to Erodion, my realtive. Give greeting to them who are in the family of Narkisus who are in the Lord.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
Give greetings to Trifena and Trifosa, these women who work in the Lord. Give greeting to my loving friend Fersis, another woman who worked very hard in the Lord. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
Give greetings to Rufus, chosen in the Lord, and to his mother, who has been a mother to me, too. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
Give greetings to Asinkritus, Flegon, Ermes, Fatrobas, Ermas, and all the other friends who are with them. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
Give greetings to Filologus and Julia, to Nereus and his sister, an to Olimfas and to all of Lord's people who are with them.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
Give greeting one another with a without.dust(holy) kiss. All Yesu's families(churches) of believers here send you.p their greetings.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
My friends, I urge you.p to watch out from those who cause divisions and put obstacles in your walking from the different teaching what you.p know. Keep away from them! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
Such people are not serving Keriso our Lord, but their own appetites. By fine talks and flattering talk they deceive innocent people. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
Everyone has heard of your.p obedience to the good talk, so I rejoice very much about you.p. I want you.p to be wise about what is good, and innocent to what is evil. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
God of peace will quickly crush S\u225?if\u232?r under your.p feet.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 The grace of our Lord Yesu will be with you.p.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
Timoti, my co-worker, sends you.p his greetings, as do Lukius, Jason, and Sosifata, my relative.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 22\~}
I, Tertius, who wrote down this letter for Fol, give greeting to you.p in the Lord.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 23\~}
Gaius, whose hospitality I and whole Yesu's family(church) here enjoy, sends you.p his greetings. Erastus, who is the city's manager of money(treasurer), and our friend Kuartus send you.p their greetings. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 24\~}
May our Lord Yesu Keriso's grace be with all of you.p. Amen.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 25\~}
God will make you.p strong, according to the good talk says. This talk about Yesu Keriso has revealed his plan for you.p Side people, this plan which was hidden from the beginning. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 26\~}
But now become clear and make known through the writings of the men who make God's knowledge(prophets) that the eternal God has commanded so that all the people in the world will truly approve(believe) and obey him.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 27\~}
To the only wise God will be big light(glory) forever through Yesu Keriso! Amen.
