\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Living by faith
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
For this reason we never deiscourage. Even though our body become without.power, but our spiritual inside man always become new. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
