\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
So we are always full of courage. We know that as long as we are at home in the body we are away from the Lord's home. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
Truly, we live here by big mind(faith), not by sight. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
We are full of courage, and would think of being away from the body and will be at home with the Lord. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
So whether we are here in the body or are away from this body, we make him please. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
All of us must stand the judgment of Keriso before him, [so that] each of us may receive what he did, good or bad in this earthly body.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Friendship with God through Keriso
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
We know what it means to fear the Lord, and so we try to persuade other people. God knows us who we are, and I think that you know in your.p hearts me clearly. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
