\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
So from now on we do not trust by worldly knowledges. If we trust Keriso in this way, we do not do so anymore. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
If anyone who is joined to Keriso is a new man. The old man is disappeared and the become new man. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
All this is done by God, who through Keriso changed us from enemies into his friends and gave us the work of making other people his friends also. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
Our good talk is that God was making all people his friends through Keriso. God did not keep an account of their sins, and he has given us good talk which tells us how he makes them his friends.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
So we are speaking for Keriso, as God himself were making talk through us. We beg on Keriso's behalf, let God change you from enemies into his friends! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
Keriso was without sin, but for our sake God made him share our sin so that are together with him that we might share the straightness of God.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 6
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
So, in our work together with God, we beg you.p who have received God's grace not to let it be wasted. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
Hear what God says:
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 \u8220?When the time came for me to show you favor,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 I heard you.
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 When the day came for me to save you,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 I helped you.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s61\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Listen! This is the time to receive God's favor. Today is the day to be saved!
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
