Although they put us sadness, but we are always glad. We are like be poor, but we make many people rich. We are like without.thing, but we really possess everything.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
Our friends in Korint! We have spoken only true talk to you.p. We have opened our hearts wide to you. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
It is not we who have closed our hearts to you.p, but it is you.p who have closed your hearts to us. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
