\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 We are the worshipping house of the living God
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
Do not work together with truly without.approving people, it cannot be done. How can straight and wrong be in partnership? How can light and darkness are one? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
How can Keriso and the S\u225?if\u232?r agree? What does a truly approving man(believer) work together with a truly approving man? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
