\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 and they shall be my people.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s61\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
And so the Lord All Mighty says,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 \u8220?You must leave them
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 and separate yourselves from them.
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Have nothing to do with what is bad,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 and I will accept you.p.
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
I will be a your Father,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 and you.p will be my sons and daughters.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 7
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
My dear friends, because these without.lying talks(promises) have been given us, let us wash ourselves from everything that makes body or soul with.dust, and let us be completely without.dust(holy) by living in fear of God.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Fol\u700?s Joy
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
Make room for us in your hearts. We have wronged no one, we have corrupted no one, nor tried to take advantage of anyone. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
I do not say this to condemn you. I have said before that you are in our hearts, and we would live or die with you. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
I am so sure of you. I take such pride in you! In all our troubles, I am still full of happiness and I am running over with joy.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
When we arrived in Makedonia, we had no rest. We have troubles everywhere, there are quarrels with other people, fears in our hearts. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
But God, who comforts when we are downhearted, comforted us by the coming of Taitus, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
not only by his coming but also his report of how you encouraged him. He told us how much you.p wait for seeing me, how sorry you have, how good you.p help me, so I am so happy.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
For even if my letter made you without.joy, I am not sorry about my writing. I could have been sorry when I saw that this letter made you.p without.joy for a while. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
But now I am happy, not because I made you.p without.joy, but because your withoout.joy thing made you.p change your.p ways. That without.joy thing was worked by God, and so we do not caused you.p problem. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
This without.joy thing that is worked by God brings a change of heart that leads us to salvation, and there is no regret in that! But worldly sadness causes death. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
See what God did with without.joy thing of yours. How earnest it has made you.p, how strong mind to make you innocence! Such anger to sin, such surprising thing, such feelings, such devotion, such readiness to punish wrongdoing! You.p have shown yourselves to be without.dust in all things.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
So I wrote that letter to you.p, it was not because of the one who did wrong or the one who was wronged. Instead, I wrote it to make clear to you.p in God's sight, how deep your.p devotion to us really is. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
