He gave us grace very much with all his wisdom and understanding. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
God did what his plan was, and put clearly to us the secret plan which he had put to finish it through Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
God's plan will fulfill when the time caught up(arrived). At that time he will make one to everything in heaven and on earth under Keriso's ruling.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
All things happened according to God's plan and will. In Keriso God chose us to be his people by his will. It was what he had decided from the beginning, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
