\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
And you.p became God's people when you heard the true talk, which the good talk brought you.p salvation. You.p truly approved(believed) in Keriso, and God put his y\u232?ru(stamp of ownership) on you.p, which is the God Spirit which he had said without.lying talk(promise). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
The God Spirit is the one that we will get what God said without.lying talk(promise) to his people, and this makes us true(gurantees) God will give us full grace to those who are his. We will lift up his big name!
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Fol talked with God(prayed) for truly approving people(believers) in Efeso
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
In this reason, since I heard about your.p big mind(faith) in the Lord Yesu and about your love for all of God's people, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
I always give thanks to God because of you.p. When(ever) I was talking with God(praying), I always ask him to help you, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
the God of our Lord Yesu Keriso, very big Father will give you the God Spirit. God Spirit will give you wisdom and put to God clear to you, so that you.p will know him. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
I am asking that your.p minds will open, so that you.p will know what is the hope to which he were called you.p, how much blessings is he promised to his people. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
You will also know how very big is his power at work in us who are the approving truth people. This power is working in us is the same as the powerful strength {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
which he raised Keriso from death and seated him at his right side in the heavenly kingdom. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
There, Keriso leads all heavenly ruling people, word power(authority), power, and lords. He has a very high name from all very high names in this world and also future world. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 22\~}
God put everything under the power of Keriso. He put Christ the ruler over all things. He made this to help his people, Yesu's family(church). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 23\~}
The Yesu's family(church) is Keriso's body, his completion who completes everything everywhere.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 2
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 God has made us alive with Keriso
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
In the past you.p were dead because of your without.hearing and sins. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
There on that time you.p followed the world's evil way, and you.p obeyed the evil spirit, powerful ruling man in the unseen world, this spirit who now leads the people who does not obey God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
Formerly, really we all were like that they are and we lived in our physical desires, we did what match with our body and minds. In our body ways we, like every people else are, will be God's anger.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
But God's mercy is without.counting(countless), and his love for us is very big, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
when we were dead in our without.hearing God brought us to life with Keriso. Only by God's grace he saved you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
In Keriso Yesu God called us with him in order to lead with him in the heaven. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
In order to show for future people the without.comparable bigness of his grace, he showed his love to us in Keriso Yesu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
Through the big mind(faith), by God's grace he saved you.p. This salvation is not from your doing, but this salvation is God's gift. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
He did not save you because of your working. So no one can boast. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
God has made us what we are, and in Keriso Yesu God made us for a life of good deeds, which this God has prepared for us to do.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Keriso has made Ju people and Side people(Gentiles) one
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
Don't forget that you are Gentiles. In fact, circumcised people insult you because you are uncircumsed people. They take pride in being circumcised. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
At that time you.p were far from Keriso. You.p were foreigners and you were not included in God's chosen people. Your.p place was not in the covenants, which were in God's without.lying talks(promises) to his people, and you.p were in this world without hope and without God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
