\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
Keriso brought us peace by making Ju people and Side people one. He destroyed that wall which seperated them and were enemies. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
