Keriso came and preached the good talk about peaceful life to all the people. He said you.p Side people, who were far away from God, and the Ju people, who were near to him. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
Through Keriso, God Spirit helps all of us, Ju people and Side people, to go to the Father.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
So you.p Side people are not foreigners or strangers any longer. You.p are now members with this nation's people with God's people and the family of God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
You.p are like a house that God is building for himself. Yesu's strength people and his people know the knowledge(prophets) are like the house posts. Yesu Keriso is like the center post. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
