Through Yesu you.p Side people also are part in building together with the Ju truly approving people(believers) in order to become God's dwelling house through his Spirit.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 3
