\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
In this reason, I, Fol, pray for you. I am in prison because I work for Keriso Yesu to help you Gentiles. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
