\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
I became a without.payment working man(servant) of the good talk by God's gift, [which] he gave me through his powerful working. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
I am very little from all God's people, but God gave me that grace to carry to the Side people the good talk about the big blessing from Keriso, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
