God made this just as his eternal plan was, which he has finished through Keriso Yesu our Lord. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
In Keriso and through our big mind(faith) to him we will be close to God without fear and with strong mind(confidence). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
Then I urge you.p not to fell down in mind because I see the hardship(I am suffering) for you.p, it is all for your. good.
