And I talk [with God] that Keriso will make his home in your.p hearts through big mind(faith). I talk [with God] that you.p will have roots and base in love, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
so that you, will be with the power to know, along with all truly approving people(believers), how wide and long, how high and deep, is Keriso's love. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
