Therefore, loving friends, as you.p always obeyed me when I was with you.p, it is so good that you.p obey me now while I am far from you.p. Continue to work with fear and trembling to finish your.p salvation. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
God always works in you.p, giving you the willingness and the power which satisfy him.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
Do all the things without.complaining or without.arguing, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
Then you.p will be without.guilt and without.dust(holy) as God's without.fault children, who live in these corruped world and evil people. You.p must shine to them like stars lighting up the heaven, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
Hold strongly to the talk of life. If you.p do these, I will be very happy about you.p on the returing day of Keriso, because this will show that all my work in you.p have not been without.meaning. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
But I will be happy if I lose my life, pour it out like a liquid sacrifice to God, as your faithful work is an offering to God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
And you.p should be glad about this and rejoice with me.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Timoti and Efafroditus
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
I am in hope in the Lord Yesu to send Timoti to you.p quickly, that I also will be encouraged when he comes back and tells me about you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
I have no other man like Timoti is, who really cares for you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
All other people look for their own desires, not the desires of Yesu Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 22\~}
But you.p know that Timoti has proved himself. Like a son with his father, we worked in the good talk. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 23\~}
I am in hope to send Timoti to you.p quickly. But first, I know what will happen to me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 24\~}
I trust the Lord that I myself will come to you.p quickly.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 25\~}
I think I must send Epaphroditus to come back to you. He is true friend in Keriso. He has worked with me to do the work for God together. We have worked hard, like soldiers. When I needed help, you sent him to me. He has helped me because of you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 26\~}
Because he wants very much to see all of you.p, he is worried because you.p heard that he was sick. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 27\~}
Yes, he was sick, and almost died, but God had mercy on him and me too, so that I would not have in sadness so much. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 28\~}
So I really want to send him to you.p so that when you.p see him, you.p can be happy, and I will not be trouble in mind about you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 29\~}
Welcome him in the Lord joyfully and give respect people like him. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 30\~}
Because he almost died for the work of Keriso, to give me the help to the work, because you.p could not help me.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 3
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 The true straight people
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
Finally, my friends, rejoice in the Lord! This doesn't bother me to write the same things to you.p I wrote at first, in fact, this is for your.p good. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
