But we are truly God's people. And this is not because someone has circumcised us. It is God Spirit that leads us to worship God. We thank God because of what Keriso Yesu has done for us. We don't think cutting our bodies is important. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
If things of the body were important, I could say I am living very well. If I were like some men who get their.p strong mind(confidence) from the things of the body, I would surpass every one of them.p {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
I was cut the skin when I was 8 days, and I am from the nation of Israil and the family of Benjamin and I am a real Ibru man. As a Farasi man, I carefully followed the law of Moses. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
And I wanted that I persecuted the Yesu's family(church). I did everything how the law were, I was without.fault. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
These all things were important to me, but now I see them without.meaning because of Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
Not only those things, I know that believing in my Lord Yesu Keriso is important, so I see all other things as without.meaning. I believe in Jesu, so I have thrown away all of those things. I saw these as rubbish and hold strongly onto Yesu Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
I am his, now I am straight with God, not because I followed the law, but because I truly approved(believed) in Keriso. God makes me straight with him by faith. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
All I want is to know Keriso and to taste the power of his rising, and to take part in his sufferings and become like him in his death, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
in this hope [that] I myself will rise from death.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Continue to get the price
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
I do not say that I have already reach to these things or become without.flaw(perfect).I am still striving to win to get the prize which Keriso Yesu has made me for him. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
My friends, I do not think that I have already got it, but the one thing I am doing is to forget what is at my back and I try to reach what is first(ahead). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
I run straight toward the end to win to get the prize, which God has called me through Keriso Yesu for the living with him in heaven.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
All of us who are spiritually grown up should think this way too. And if you.p think differently about these things, God will put them clear to you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
