My friends, all of you.p should try to follow thing I am doing, and watch well other people who lived that way we showed you. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
I have told you.p this many times before, and now I repeat it with tears: here are many people living as enemies to Keriso's the cross. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
To the end, God will destroy them, they do whatever their bodies want, they are proud of the shameful acts, and they think only about earthly things. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
But our village is heaven, and we are waiting for him our Saving man the Lord Yesu Keriso, will come from heaven. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
By his power to rule all things, he will change our weak bodies and change them like his own very good body.
