Show doing patient things to others and so all the people recognize this. The Lord is coming not.far(soon). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
Don't be trouble in mind(worry) about anything, but in all your talking with God(prayers) ask God for what you.p want, always ask him with thankful hearts. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
And God's peace, which is so high from people's understanding, will protect your.p hearts and minds in Keriso Yesu.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
Finally, my friends, fill your.p minds about good things. Think about these things which are true, respectful, straight, without.fault, lovely and honorable. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
Keep putting into action all what you.p learned and received from me, both in my talks and in my actions. Then God who gives us peace will be with you.p.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Fol's thanks for their gifts
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
I so rejoiced in the Lord that you.p want to help me again. You wanted to help me before. But you have no other way to help me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
I am not talking because I am in need. I have learned to be satisfied with what I have. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
When there is nothing, I know about that. When there is plenty, I know about that too. I learned this secret thing, so that all the places, at any time, I am enough/o.k, whether I am full or hungry, whether I have plenty or only few. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
I can do everything through Keriso who gives me strength.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
But this was really good for you.p to involve in my troubles. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
You people in Filifi know that you.p already helped me first. That was the time when I started to preach good talk. When I left Makedonia province, you were the only Yesu's group(church) who helped me with money. No other church did that. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
When I was in Tesalonika, many times you.p sent me things I need to help. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
This is not that I want to receive gifts from you.p, but I want you to do good things so that God will bless you through rewarding you back. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
And now I have everything and plenty! I have all what I need, because Efafroditus brought your.p gift to me. These are like the sweet smelling sacrifice offered to God who accepts, and are pleased to God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
And my God will give you all your.p needs from very big riches in Keriso Yesu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
God our Father's name should be very big forever. Amen.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Fol's final greeting talk
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
Give my kissing(greeting) talk to all those who are God's people in Keriso Yesu. People who truly approve(believers) here with me send you.p their greeting talk. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 22\~}
