Be careful your action wisely toward those who are not approving truth people(believers), do good every working you.p have with them. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
Your.p talk should always be pleasant and joyable, so that you will give the straight answer to every people.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Final kissing(greeting) talk
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
Tukikus will tell you.p all the talk about me. He is my friend, a without.payment working man(servant) with big mind(faith) with us in the Lord. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
I am sending him to you.p so that you.p will know how we.p are living here and he will encourage your.p hearts. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
He is coming with Onesimus, our faithful friend, who is also one of you.p. They.d will tell you.p everything what is happening here.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
Aristakus, who entered in darkness house with me, sends greeting talk, and Mak also, who is the cousin of Banabas. (You have heard the talk about him, when he comes to you.p, welcome him.) {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
Yesu, whom they call J\u232?stus, also sends greeting talk. These three people are the only Ju people among my working men into the ruling of God, and they have been a big helpful men to me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
Efafras, who is one of you.p and a without.payment working man(servant) of Keriso Yesu, sends greeting talk. He always stands in talking with God(prayer) for you.p, so that you.p will stand strongly to the will of God, as strong people who truly approve(believers) in Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
I testify about him he is working hard for you.p and for those who are at Laodikea place and Ierafolis place. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
Our friend Luk, who is a doctor, and Demas, they.d send greeting talk to you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
Give my greeting talk to them friends at Laodikea place, and to woman Nimfa and the Yesu's family(church) who gather in her house.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
After you.p read this letter, you.p must know that it is also read in the Yesu's family(church) at Laodikea. At the same time, read my letter to the approving truth people(believers) in Laodikea place they will send it to you.p.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
Tell Akifus: \u8220?Finish that work which Lord give you.s.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
I, Fol, write this greeting talk in my own hand. Remember to pray for me while I am in the darkness house. Grace be with you.p.
