You.p know how badly they treat us in Filifi region, before we came to you.p we had held strong suffering there. But our God gave us power to preach his good talk to widely to you.p without.fear even though we enemy surrounded us. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
