We begged you.p, we encouraged you.p and urged you.p to live good lives in this way how God wants. Because God called you.p into his kingdom and big light(glory).
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
Therefore, we will not stop thanks talk to God, when you.p received his good talk from us, you.p didn't think about our talk as the talk from people's thought, but really the talk of God is, which is at work in you.p who truly approve(believe). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
Friends, you.p became imitating people of Yesu's families(churches) in Judia, which are in Keriso Yesu. Your.p people put in suffering to you the same things those the Ju people put the Yesu's families(churches). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
They killed the Lord Yesu and the God's people who make know(prophets), and also have persecuted us. They became without.joy to God and also people without.joy. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
They tried to stop preaching good saving talk to the Side people. In this way they always piled up their sin on top. But God's anger has come on them later.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Fol's desiring to see the Tesalonika people
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
Friends, after we were seperated from you.p for a short time(but our heart don't leave you.p), we try to make effort to go to see you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
We really wanted to go to you.p, I, Fol tried to go back again and again, but S\u225?if\u232?r were stopping us. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
For what gives hope and joy to us, and what will be our reward and the crown in which we will stand together when our Lord Yesu comes? It is you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
Yes, You.p are our big light(glory) and joy.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 3{\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
So we were not able to bear this thing long, we decided to stay on by ourselves in Aten. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
We sent Timoti, who is our friend and God's working man who made the talk of Keriso wide. We sent him to give power and encourage you.p who you.p are standing with a big mind(faith). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
In order that no one should be shaken in these persecutions. You.p know that he has chosen us for these persecutions. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
When we were with you.p, we have told to you.p that they will persecute us. And that is exactly what happened as you.p know. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
In this reason, I had sent Timoti. I could not bear long, so I send to check your.p big mind(faith). I was afraid that some way S\u225?if\u232?r tempted you.p and our work had been without.meanining.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Timoti's encouraging report
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
But when Timoti had come back, he brought good talk to us about your.p big mind(faith) and love. He told that you.p always remembered our visit with joy, that you.p want to see us just as we want to see you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
Therefore, friends, in all our pain and suffering, we have became strong about you.p because of your.p big mind(faith). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
Because now we really live if you.p are standing strongly in the Lord. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
How we thank God for you! Because of you we have great joy as we enter God's presence. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
In night and day we ask him with all our heart to let us see you.p again and give what is lacking in your.p big mind(faith).
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
May our Father God himself and our Lord Yesu prepare the way for us to come to you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
May the Lord make your.p love increase and spread out for each other and for every people, just as our love spread out for you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
In the same way he will make you.p strong, and you.p will be without.reason and without.dust(holy) in the presence of our Father God when our Lord Yesu comes with all who belong to him.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 4
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 A life which makes God joy
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
Friends, finally we taught you.p how to live in order to make God joy, as already you.p are living. Now we ask you.p and urge you.p in the name of the Lord Yesu to do continually. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
For you.p know what we taught you.p by the power of the Lord Yesu.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
God want you.p should be without.dust(holy), so you.p should avoid sexual immorality. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
You.p should know how to live with your.p wife in a without.dust(holy) and respectful way, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
don't fill with sexual thought like earthly people, who do not know God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
In this thing, none of you.p should do wrong his friends or make them doing sin. The Lord will put in suffering all people about theose sins, as we strongly told you.p before. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
God did not call us to live in sinful life, but to live a without.dust(holy) life. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
Whoever rejects this teaching talk is not to a man, but to God, who gives you.p God Spirit.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
There is no thought for us to write to you.p about love each other, because only God have taught you.p about loving each other. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
In fact, you.p have overflow your.p love to all friends throughout Makedonia area. Friends, but we beg you.p to love them so much. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
Keep doing this loving work with a quiet life, you.p keep on working hard with your.p hands, as we have encouraged you.p before, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
so that other people who are not believers will respect you.p, and you.p will not depend on any people for what you.p need.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Lord's coming
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
Friends, we want you.p to know what will happen to the believers who died, so that you.p will not in sadness like as people who have no hope. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
For we truly approve(believe) that Yesu died and rose to life, so we truly approve(believe) that when Yesu come back, God will bring back to life with Yesu the believers who have died.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
What we are teaching you.p now is the Lord's teaching: we who are alive on this day the Lord comes will not go ahead of those who have died. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
Then the Lord himself will come down from heaven, with the voice of the head man carrying heavenly message(angels) and with the trumpet call of God, and the dead people in Keriso will rise first. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
After that, we who are still alive and left will meet together with them in the clouds in order that we meet the Lord in the sky. So we will be with the Lord forever. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
Therefore encourage one another with these talks.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 5
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
Friends, there is no thought for us to write you.p when and which days will happen. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
For you.p know well the day of the Lord will come surprisingly, like as a stealing man will come in the night. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
When people say, "All the things are peace and safety," then suddenly pains will come on them as pains comes on a pregnant woman, and there will be no escape.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
Friends, but you.p are not in darkness about this things happening and you.p will not surprised when Lord's day come like a stealing man come. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
You.p are all children of the light and children of the day. We do not belong to the night or to the darkness. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
So then, let us not be like others, who are asleep, but you.p should be awake and watch out. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
At night people should sleep, and at night they become drunk. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
But who we are in the light will watch out, we will put on big mind(faith) and love as a breast protecting cloth and the hope of salvation as a hat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
God did not choose us to come into his anger but we receive salvation through our Lord Yesu Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
Keriso died for us, whether living or died when Yesu comes, we may live together with him. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
Should encourage one another and help same way, just as now you.p are doing.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Fol's final instructions
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
Friends, respect those who are your.p leading menin the Lord's work. They work hard among you.p and give you spiritual guidance. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
Show them big respect and love because of their work. Live in peace.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
Friends, we beg you.p to warn who are without.moving(idly). Encourage you.p who are afraid. Help those who are weak. Be patient with every people. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
Don't pay back with wrong, but always do good to other people and to every people.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
Always be in joy. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
Talk with God always. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
Be thankful in all things, because this is God's will for you.p in Keriso Yesu.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
Don't extinguish the fire of the God Spirit. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
Do not deny inspired talks, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
but put in the test everything that is said; hold this talk which is good, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 22\~}
reject all evil things.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 23\~}
May the God who gives us peace make you.p without.dust(holy) in every way. May your.p spirit, mind and body be kept without.blame at the coming of our Lord Yesu Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 24\~}
God will do this thing, because God who called you.p is full of big mind(faithful).
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 25\~}
Friends, talk with God for us. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 26\~}
Greet all friends with the love. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 27\~}
I urge you.p by the name of the Lord to read this letter to all friends.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 28\~}
The grace of our Lord Yesu Keriso be with you.p.
\page
\par\pard\plain \s0\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 2TH - - Nama Back Translation
\par\pard\plain \s93\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb40\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs46 Fol's second letter to the people of Tesalonika
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 1
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
This letter is from them Fol, Sail\u232?s and Timoti. We are writing to the Yesu's family(church) in Tesalonika in our Father God and the Lord Yesu Keriso:
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
May the Father God and the Lord Yesu Keriso give you.p grace and peace.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Thanksgiving and talking with God
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
Friends, we must give thanks to God at all times for you.p. This is straight for us to do, because your.p big mind(faith) is growing so much and the love which all of you.p has for the other people is growing so much. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
In this reason we ourselves keep on speaking well about you.p in the Yesu's families(churches) of God. We keep on speaking well how you.p endure and truly approve(believe) through all the persecutions and sufferings which you.p are seeing.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
All this thing approves that God\u700?s judgment is straight, and so that you.p will be able to be to the ruling of God, because of this you.p are in suffering. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
God is straight: He will put them in trouble to those who put you.p in trouble. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
And God will give rest to you.p who are in trouble, and to us as well. He will do this when the Lord Yesu appears from heaven with his powerful men carrying heavenly message(angels), {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
with a flaming fire, to put in pain those who reject God and those who do not obey the good talk about our Lord Yesu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
He will put them in final pain forever, separated from the Lord and from his power with big light. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
When he comes he will receive big light(glory), and honor from his approving truth people. You.p will be there among them honor Yesu in these days, because you.p have truly approved(believed) what we told you.p about him.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
Therefore, we continue to talk with God(pray) for you.p that our God will make you.p true life to where he called you.p. We talk with God that God will do by his power all your.p desire and work of big mind(faith). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
As a result, people will praise our Lord Jesus because of how you live. You also will receive praise, because you belong to Jesus. All this is possible because the grace of our God and the Lord Jesus Christ.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 2
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 What thing will happen in close Yesu's coming
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
Friends, we will say about coming again of our Lord Yesu Keriso and how all of us will gather together to meet him. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
Don't be shaken or alarmed by those who say that Lord's coming has reached. Don't truly approve(believe) them if they claim that they have seen a eye passover thing(vision), or revealing talk, or a letter came from us. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
Do not let anyone deceive you in any way. For that day will not come until there is a big fight against God and the man of without.law appear, whom God will destroy. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
He will oppose and will lift himself over everything that people call god and every object of worship. He will sit in God\u700?s worshipping house, claiming that he himself is God.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
Rememer how I tell you.p when I was with you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
And you.p know what is holding him back, so that he may appear when his day comes. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
For this without.law work is already at work secretly, and it will remain secret until the one who is holding it back stepts out of the place. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
Then the without.law man will appear, whom the Lord Yesu will kill with the breath of his mouth and destroy him by the big light(glory) of his coming. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
This evil man will come to do the work with lying power of S\u225?if\u232?r and showing things(signs) and surprisong things(wonders). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
He will do different shape of evil lying thing to deceive them who are to the punishment, because they refused to love and accept the truth that would save them. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
For this reason God sends them a powerful deceive to them so that they will truly approve(believe) these lies. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
So he will put them in pain who have not truly approved(believed) the true talk but caused doing evils.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Stand firm
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
As for us we continue to give thanks to God in the reason of you.p, loving friends whom Lord loves. We are always giving thanks that God chose you.p to be among them who are the first, to know salvation which came through God Spirit who makes you.p without.dust(holy) and through your.p truly approvement(belief) in the truth. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
He called you.p to salvation when we told you.p the good talk; now you.p can share in the big light(glory) of our Lord Yesu Keriso.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
My friends, be all these in mind, stand firm and hold fast on what we taught you by preaching and by letter.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
May our Lord Yesu Keriso and God our Father, who loved us and by his grace gave us eternal living help and a good hope, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
comfort your.p heart and give power in every good thing what you.p do and say.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 3
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Talk with God for us
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
Finally, my loving friends, we ask you.p to talk with God for us. Talk with God firstly that the Lord's talk will become wide rapidly and be honored wherever it goes, just as how it came to you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
Talk with God, too, that he save us from wicked and evil people, for all the people are not approving truth people(believer).
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
But the Lord is very big mind(faithful) and he will make you.p strong and guard you.p from the evil man. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
And we are mind strong(confident) in the Lord that you.p started doing this which we had said and will do always. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
God will take you into a deep knowledge to the love of God and the endurance which comes from Keriso.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Encourage to good living
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
Loving friends, we give you.p this commanding talk in the name of our Lord Yesu Keriso: Stay away from all approving truth people who keep on living only seating and don't follow this teaching which we gave them. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
You.p know that you.p should follow our action. We were not idle when we were with you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
We never accepted food from other people without payment. We worked day and night so that we would not be a burden to any of you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
There are the authority to us that we can ask you.p for food, but we didn't, in order that we wanted to give you.p that way you.p will follow. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
Even while we were with you.p, we gave you.p this command: \u8220?The one who do not work shall not eat.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
But we keep on hearing that some of you.p are living without working lives, refusing to work and eating time to keep on only walking around people. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
In the name of the Lord Yesu Keriso we sent these people and said to them to live good and to work for their food to eat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
My friends, but you.p never get tired of doing good.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
See those people careful who refuse to obey what we say in our letter. Stay away from them so that they will be full of shame. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
Don't see them as enemies are, but warn them as men who truly approve(believers) are.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Fol's final greeting talk
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
May the Lord of peace himself give you.p his peace at all times and in every situation. The Lord be with you.p all.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
Here is my greeting talk which is in my own handwriting. Fol, I used to write simple writing when I write in the end of all letter in order to prove that this letter came from me.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
May the grace of our Lord Yesu Keriso be with you.p all.
