\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 About false teaching
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
I want you.s to stay in Efeso city, just as I asked you.s when I was on the trip to Makedonia province. Some people there are in false teaching, and you.s must tell them to stop. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
