The meaning of this command is love which comes from a without.dust heart, a bright conscience, and a strong big mind(faith). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
Some people have turned away from these straight way and have lost their way in without.meaning discussions. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
They want to be teaching men of the law. They speak very strongly, but they do not know what they said.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
