We will find that teaching in the good talk which he gave me to tell, this good talk from big light(glorious) and blessed God.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Lord's grace to Fol
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
I give thanks to Keriso Yesu our Lord, who has given me strength for my work. I give thanks to him who had made me with meaning and appointed for woking for him. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
This passing time was I spoke evil talk to him and persecuted and insulted him. But God was full of mercy to me because I did not yet have big mind(faith) and did not know what I was doing. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
