This talk is a true so that we accepted completely and truly approved(believed): Keriso Yesu came into this world to save sinners. I was really bad sinner and I surpassed all men {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
But God was merciful to me in order that Keriso Yesu might show his patience in dealing with me, the very bad sinners, as an example for those who would later be men who truly approve(believe) him and receive eternal life. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
To the eternal Ruling man(King), without.dead and without.seeing, the only God himself\u8212?only to him be honor and big light(glory) forever! Amen.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
Timoti, my son, I truly approve(believe) you in this command, according to the talks that God's people who make know(prophets) spoke in the past about you.s. Fight well with these talks as arrows in order to fight well, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
and keep on holding your.s big mind(faith) and a bright conscience. Some people have not been listening to their conscience and have made a without.meaning of their big mind(faith). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
Among them are Imaneus and Aleksanda, whom I have gave them to the power of S\u225?if\u232?r; this will teach them to stop saying evil talk to God.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 2
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Yesu's family(church) worship
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
First of all, my encouraging talk is that all asking, talking with God, talking with God for other people, and thanksgivings be offered to God for all people. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
Pray for kings and all rulers who are in power, so that we may live a quiet and peaceful life with all godly life(godliness) and without. dust(holiness). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
This is good and it pleases God our Savior. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
And he wants to save all people. He wants everyone to know his message and to accept it as true. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
For there is one God and one middleman between God and man, Keriso Yesu he himself, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
who gave himself to save all the people. That was the proof at the straight time God will save every people. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
And in this reason he sent me as a man with Yesu's authority(apostle) and teaching man of the Side people, to preach the talk of big mind(faith) and truth. I am not lying. I am telling the truth!
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
