Women should learn in silence and all humility. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
I do not allow women to teach and to receive power from men. They must keep quiet. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
For Ed\u232?m was created first and later If. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
And it was not Ed\u232?m who was deceived by S\u225?if\u233?r, but the woman deceived and broke God's law. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
