A man must know how to take care of his own family. If he cannot do that, he will not be able to take care of God's people in the Yesu's family(church). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
He must be mature in the big mind(faith), so that he will not be in high himself, he would receive punishment, as the S\u225?if\u232?r received. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
He should be a man who people outside the Yesu's family(church) respect him, so that he will not be shameful and fall into the S\u225?if\u232?r's trap.
