\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
The God Spirit says clearly that some people will leave the big mind(faith) in the end; they will obey lying spirits and follow the teachings of S\u225?if\u232?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
