because the talk of God and the talking with God make it well to God.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 A good without.payment working man(servant) of Keriso Yesu
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
If you.s give these teaching talks to the approving truth people, you.s will be a good worker of Keriso Yesu, you.s should feed yourself spiritually on the talks of this big mind(faith) and in the true teaching which you.s have followed. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
