We fight and work hard, because we have placed our hope in the living God, who is the Savior of all people, and especially of those who approve truth(believe).
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
