Do not neglect the spiritual gift which is in you.s, which he gave to you.s when the God's people who make know(prophets) spoke and the Yesu's family(church) head men laid their hands on you.s. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
