\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Trial and temptation
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
My friends, rejoice when many trials come to you.p, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
because you.p know that the tamptation of your.p big mind(faith) produces endure. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
