\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Hearing and doing
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
My loving friends, remember this: Everyone must be quick to listen, but delay speaking and delay to become angry. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
Human anger does not carry the straight life that God desires. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
Therefore, take away every bad things and wicked action. Obey to God and accept the talk that he plants in your.p hearts, which will save you.p.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 22\~}
Do not only listen to the talk, and deceive yourselves. Do how it says. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 23\~}
