\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 26\~}
If you.p say you.p are religious but you.p do not control your.p tongues, you.p deceive yourselves and your.p religion is without.meaning. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 27\~}
