\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
You.p do well if you.p obey the law of the God's kingdom in the Buk(scripture), \u8220?Love your friend as yourself.\u8221? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
