because judgment without mercy will be shown to anyone who has not been merciful. Mercy surpasses judgment.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Faith and Actions
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
My friends, what is good if someone boasts about big mind(faith) but has not actions? Can that big mind(faith) save you.p? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
To illustate, if you.p know anyone who has not clothes and food. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
