\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Show me your.s big mind(faith) without deeds, and I will show you.s my big mind(faith) by my deeds. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
