My friends, can a fig tree can bear olives, or a grapevine bear figs? A salty water hole cannot produce fresh water.
\par\pard\plain \s106\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Two kinds of Wisdom
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
