\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 4
\par\pard\plain \s106\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Submit Yourselves to God
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
What causes fights and quarrels among you.p? These come from your.p bodily desires that fight in you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
