\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Grace and peace to you.p from him who is, who always was, and who is still to come, from the 7 spirits who are before his throne, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
