\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 It was like the Son of Men
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
I am Jon, your.p brother. Because we belong to Yesu' ruling, we are having trouble and pain. So, we all need to be strong and patient, as Yesu helps us. I was there on the island of Fatmos, because I was preached talk about God and Yesu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
