His feet were bright like a melt and refined steal and his voice was like many rainfall. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
In his right hand he held 7 stars, and from his mouth came out bothside sharp knife(sword), and his face shone like a strong sun are shining. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
When I saw him, I fell at his feet like a dead man. He put his right hand and said, "Don't be afraid. I am the first and the last. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
I am who is alive! Who was dead, and now I am alive forever! To me there are keys of death an fire(hades) {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
Therefore write what you.s have seen, what is now and what will happen later. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
