\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 "This talk is from him who holds 7 stars in his right hand, and he who walks around 7 gold lampstands place. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
