\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 To the Yesu's family(church) in Sadis
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
Write this letter to man carrying heavenly message of the Yesu's family(church) in Sadis:
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 This talk is from him who has the 7 spirits of God and the 7 stars. I know everything what you.p are doing. People think and say that you are alive. But this is not true, because you are dead. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
Get up! Your.p belief has become not strong and almose died. So then you.p must strengthen your.p belief. Because I have found your.p deeds is without.flaw(perfect) to my God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
Remember what you.p have got and heard; hold to it strongly and turn back from your sins. If you.p don't wake up, I will come upon you.p like a thief, and you.p don't know which day I will come upon you.p.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
But you.p have a few people in Sadis who don't make their clothes dirty. They will walk with me white clothes, because they are enough. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
Those who win will be clothed white clothes. I will never erase their names from the book of life. But I will make know in front of my Father and his men carrying heavenly message(angels) that they are mine. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
Whoever has ears, must listen to what God Spirit says to Yesu's families(churches).
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 To the Yesu's family(church) in Filadelfia
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
Write this letter to the man carrying heavenly message of the Yesu's family(church) in filadelfia:
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 This talk is from him who is without.dust(holy) and true. He is the one who has the key of Deifid. When he opens the door, no one can close it, and when he closes door, no one can open it. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
I know all your.p deeds, and I have opened the door for you.p no one can close it. I know you.p have little strength, but you.p obey my talk and have not denied my name. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
Listen! Who is S\u225?if\u233?r's group, those liars who say that they are Jews but are not, I will make them come [and] bow down at your.p feet. They will know all that I love you.p. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
Because you.p have kept my command with endurance, I will also protect you.p from the day of trial that will happen on the whole world to test all the people on earth. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
I am coming back quickly. Hold here on to what you.p have, so that no one will take your.p crown. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
Those who win will became post of the worshipping house of God and they will stay there forever and I will write on them my God's name and the name of the God's city, new Jerusalem, which is coming down out of heaven from my God. I will also write on them my new name. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
Whoever has ears, must listen to what God Spirit says to the Yesu's families(churches).
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 To the Yesu's family(church) in Laodikia
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
Write this letter to the man carrying heavenly message of the Yesu's family(church) in Laodikia:
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 This talk is from him who is Amen, faithful and true watching man, the foundation of God's creation. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
I know your.p deeds, that you.p are neither cold nor hot. I want you.p are cold or hot! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
But you.p are without sweet/tasty-neither hot nor cold, I will spit out of my mouth! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
You.p say, 'I am rich; I have all the things what I need. But you.p don't know that you.p are unhappy, shameful, poor, blind and naked. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
I advise you.p to take gold from me gol which is refined in the fire, you.p can become rich. And also buy white clothes so that you.p will not feel a shame of your.p nakedness. And take tree oil for your.p eyes so that you.p can see. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
I rebuke and discipline all people whom I love. Take thought(lesson) and turn from your.p sins. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
Look! I stand here at the door and knock. When you.p hear my voice and open the door, I will go into, and we will eat together.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
I will invite all the people who win so that they sit with me in my ruling sitting place, just as I have become winner and I sat with my Father on his ruling sitting place. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 22\~}
Whoever has ears, must listen to what God Spirit says to the Yesu's families(churches).
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 4
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Worship in heaven
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
After this I was looking, and there was an open door in heaven. And the voice I had first heard speaking to me like the sound of a trumpet said, "Come up here, and I will show you.p what must happen after this." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
Immediately I was in God Spirit, and there was before me a ruling sitting place(throne) in heaven a someone sitting on there. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
Who sat on the ruling sitting place(throne) shined like a green stone and red stone, and there is a rainbow which shined brightly encircled his ruling sitting place(throne). {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
Other 24 ruling sitting places(thrones) sorrounded him, and 24 head people sat on them. They were all clothed in white clothes, and had gold crowns on their heads. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
From the ruling sitting place came flashes of lightning and roaring of thunder. In the front of ruling sitting place, there were 7 torches, which are 7 spirits of God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
In the front of those ruling sitting place there was like a sea of glass shining.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 In the middle, around the ruling sitting place, were 4 living things, covered with eyes in front and the back {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
The first living thing looked like a big wild cat(lion), the second was a cow, and the third had a face like a human; the 4th looked like an flying egale. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
Those 4 thing had 6 wings, and was covered with their eyes, inside and out wings. Day and night they never stop saying:
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Without.dust, without.dust(holy), without.dust(holy) is the Lord God Almighty,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 he who was, who is, and who is to come."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
When those living things praise and honor ang give thanks to him who sits on the ruling sitting place and who live forever, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
those 24 head people kneel down and worship him who live forever and they put their crowns in front of the ruling sitting place and say,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
" O Lord our God, you.s are enough
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 to take big light(glory) and honor and power,
