Then I saw the book on the right hand of the one who sits on the ruling sitting place; letters was covered from inside and outside in that book, and was sealed with 7 seals.(Note: people use this after closing storage.) {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
