So I started crying because I can't see any one who can open that book and read it. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
But one of 24 head people he said to me, "Don't cry! Look, the Big wild cat(Lion) from Juda's family, the Descendant of Deifid, can do, he can open that book and its 7 seals.
