When he took the book, the 4 living things and 24 head people fell down before the Lamb. They had a music tool like a guitar and gold bowls filled with sacrifice of the talking with God of God's people. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
And they sang a new song with saying:
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 "You.s are able to take this book
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 and to open this sealed book.
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 You.s were killed, and by your.s blood had done payment for God
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 people from the every group(tribe) and several talk(language) and people(many people) and every nation.
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
And you.p have made them to be a God's ruling and its burning sacrifice men(priests)
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 and they will be ruler on earth."
