Again a talk came from the ruling sitting place, saying,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 \u8220?Praise our God,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 all you.p his without.payment working people,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 you.p who fear him
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 all big and small!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
Then I heard sound like a crowd's shouting, like the sound of a roaring waterfall and like loud peals of thunder,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 \u8220?Praise God!
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Because the Lord, our Almighty God reigns!
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
Let us rejoice and be glad
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 and give him big light(glory)!
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Because the wedding with the Lamb has come,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 and his bride has prepared herself.
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
Fine cloth, bright and clean, was given to her to wear."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Because the cloth shows for the good deeds of God's people.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
Then the man carrying heavenly message said to me, \u8220?Write this: Blessed are those who have been invited to the wedding feast of the Lamb.\u8221? And he said to me again, \u8220?These are the true talks of God.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
Then I fell down at his feet to worship him, but he said to me, \u8220?Don't do this! I am only a worker together with you.s and with other approving truth people, all those who hold to the approving truth Yesu revealed. Worship God!\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 Because the testimony to Yesu is God Spirit of approving truth.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 The rider sit on the white horse
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
I saw heaven open, and there was standing a white horse. Its rider which is called Faithful and True, it is with straight he judges and makes war. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
His eyes were like a flame of fire, and he wore many crowns on his head. He had a name written on him, no one knows these lettters but himself. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
He is dressed in a cloth dipped in blood, and his name is The Word of God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
The armies of heaven followed him, riding on white horses and dressed in fine cloth, white and clean. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
From his mouth came a sharp sword, with which he will defeat the nations. He will rule over them with the ruling man(king)'s stick of iron. He will trample them in the alcohol press of the furious anger of the Almighty God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
On his cloth and on his thigh was written the name: \u8220?Ruling man(King) of ruling men(kings) and Lord of lords.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
Then I saw a man carrying heavenly message standing on the sun, who shouted in a loud voice to all the birds flying in the sky: \u8220?Come, gather together for God's big feast, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
so that you.p may eat the flesh of ruling men(kings), of soldiers heading people, and of soldiers, of horses and of their riders, and the flesh of all people, without.payment working men(servants) and free men, small men to big men!\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
Then I saw the big crocodile and the ruling men(kings) of the earth and their armies gathered together to fight against the one who was riding the horse and his army. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
But the big crocodile was captured, and together with his false God's man who make know(prophet) who had done false special workings(miracles) in his presence. By his special workings(miracles) he deceived those who had the mark of the big crocodile and those who had worshiped his image. These two were both thrown alive into burning fire with sulfur. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
And the rest were killed by the both side sharp sword which comes out of his mouth of the one who was riding the horse, and all the birds were completly full their flesh eating.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 20
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 1,000 years
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
Then I saw a man carrying heavenly message coming down from heaven, holding in his hand the key of the without.end hole and a heavy chain. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
He held the dragon, that ancient snake, that is, the Devil, or S\u225?if\u232?r, and chained him up for a thousand years. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
The man carrying heavenly message threw him into the without.end hole, and locked it, and made it very tight, so that he could not deceive the nations any more until the thousand years were over. After that he must be set loose for a little while.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
Then I saw ruling sitting places, and those who sat on them were given the power to judge. And I saw the spirits of those who had been killed because of their testimony about Yesu and because of the talk of God. They had not worshiped the big crocodile or its image, nor had they received the mark of the big crocodile on their foreheads or their hands. They came to life and reigned with Keriso for 1,000 years. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
(The rest of the dead people did not come to life until 1,000 years were over.) This is the first raising of the dead. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
Blessed and without.dust(holy) are those who are included in this first raising of the dead. The second death has no power over them, but they shall be burning sacrifice men(priests) of God and of Keriso also and they will rule with him for 1,000 years.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 They defeated S\u225?if\u232?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
When 1,000 years pass over, S\u225?if\u232?r will be set loose from his darkness house, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
and he will go out to deceive the nations in the four corners of the earth, Gog and Makok. S\u225?if\u233?r will gather them for battle, the number they are like the sand on the seashore. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
They spread out over the earth and surrounded the shelters of God's people and his loving city. But fire came down from heaven and burned them. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
Then the S\u225?if\u232?r, who deceived them, was thrown into burning place with fire and with sulfur, where the big crocodile and the false God's man who make know(prophet) had already been thrown. They will be in suffering day and night forever.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 The dead people will be judged
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
Then I saw a big white ruling sitting place and the one who sits on it. Earth and heaven passed over from his presence and there was no place for them. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
And I saw the dead people, big and small, standing before the ruling sitting place. Books were opened, and then another book was opened, which is the book of the living. The dead people were judged according to what they had done, which had been recorded in the books. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
The sea brought up all the dead people who were in it. Death and the dead people's place called Ades brought up all the dead people who were there too. Then God judged each person. God saw what they had done and he decided what was right. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
Then death and Ades were thrown into wide fire(the lake of fire). This wide fire is the second death. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
Those who did not have their name written in the book of the living were thrown into the lake of fire.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 21
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 The new heaven and the new earth
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
Then I saw a new heaven and a new earth. The first heaven and the first earth passed away, and the sea no left there. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
I saw the Without.dust City, the new Jerusalem, coming down out of heaven from God, prepared, as a bride beautifully dressed for her husband. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
And I heard a loud voice speaking from the ruling sitting place saying: \u8220?Now God's home is with his people! He will live with them, and they shall be his people. God himself will be with them, and he will be their God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
He will wipe away all tears from their eyes. There will be no more death, no more grief or crying or pain, because the old things have passed away.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
He who sits on the ruling sitting place said, \u8220?Now I make all things new!\u8221? He also said to me, \u8220?Write this, because these talks can be trusted and true.\u8221? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
And he said to me, \u8220?It is done! I am the first and the last, the beginning and the end. To anyone who is thirsty I will give water to drink from the spring of the water of life without paying for it. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
Those who are winner will receive all this from me: I will be their God, and they will be my children. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
But very scaring people, men who give teeth(betrayers), who lost their truly approve(believe), murderers, the immoral, and those who practice sorcery, those who worship idols and all liars\u8212?their place is the burning place with fire and sulfur, which is the second death.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 The New Jerusalem
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
One of the 7 men carrying heavenly message(angels) who had the 7 bowls full of last fearful suffering things came and said to me, \u8220?Come, I will show you.s new married woman, which is the wife of the Lamb.\u8221? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
And he carried me away in God Spirit to the top of a very high mountain, and showed me the Without.dust City, Jerusalem, coming down out of heaven from God. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
It has the big light(glory) of God, and its brilliance was like a precious stone, a white and clear stone as glass. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
It had a big, high stone fence with 12 gates and with 12 men carrying heavenly message(angels) in charge of the gates. On these gates were written the names of the 12 tribes of Israil. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
There were three gates on the east, three on the south, three on the north, and three on the west. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
This city's stone fence was built on 12 big stones, on which were written the names of the 12 men with Yesu's authority(apostles) of the Lamb. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
The man carrying heavenly message who spoke to me had a gold measuring stick to measure that city, its gates, and its stone fence. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
The city have exactly same length and width. He measured the city with this measuring stick and it was about 2,200 km long, same wide and same high. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
He measured the wall outside and it was about 65 mit\u232? thick, according to human measure which a man carrying heavenly message used. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
The wall was made white stone, and the city was made of very good gold, like glass. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
The foundation stones of the city wall were adorned with all kinds of precious stones. The first foundation stone was jaspa, the second safair\u232?, the third ageit, the 4th emerald, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
the 5th oniks, the 6th kanalian, the 7th krisolit, the 8th beril, the 9th tofaj, the 10th Krisofrase, the eleventh jasint, the 12th ametist. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 21\~}
The 12 gates were 12 pearls; each gate was made from a single pearl. And the street of the city was of pure gold, like a glass.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 22\~}
I did not see a worshipping house in that city, because the Lord God Almighty and the Lamb they are their worshipping house. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 23\~}
That city has no need of the sun or the moon to shine on it, because the big light(glory) of God gives light, and the Lamb is its lamp. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 24\~}
The peoples of the nations will walk in its light, and the ruling men(kings) of the earth will bring their big light(glory) into it. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 25\~}
On day gates will not be shut, because there will be no night there. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 26\~}
All the nations will bring their big light(glory) and honor into that city. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 27\~}
But nothing that is evil will enter the city, nor these people who do shameful things or tells lies, but only those whose names are written in the Lamb's book of the living.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs42 22
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 The river with the water of life
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 1\~}
Then the man carrying heavenly message showed me the river of the water of life, as clear as glass, flowing from the ruling sitting place of God and of the Lamb {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 2\~}
there in the middle of the big street of the city and on each side of the river stood the tree of life, bearing 12 crops of fruit, yielding its fruit every month. And the leaves of these tree are for the making good(healing) of the nations. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 3\~}
There will not curse any more. The ruling sitting place of God and of the Lamb will be in the city, and his without.payment working people will worship him. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 4\~}
They will see his face, and his name will be written on their foreheads. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 5\~}
There will be no more night. They will not look for the light of a lamp or the light of the sun, because the Lord God will be their light. And they will reign forever.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 The coming of Yesu
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 6\~}
The man carrying heavenly message said to me, \u8220?These talks are trustworthy and true. The Lord God, who gives God Spirit to the God's people who make know(prophets), has sent his man carrying heavenly message to show to his without.payment working people what must happen not.far.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 7\~}
\u8220?Watch out! I am coming not.far! Blessed is the one who keeps the prophetic talks in this book!\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 8\~}
I, Jon, am the one who heard and saw these things. And when I heard and seen them, I fell down to worship at the feet of the man carrying heavenly message who had been showing these things to me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 9\~}
But he said to me, \u8220?Don\u700?t do that! I am a without.payment working man like you.s are and with your.s friends God's people who make know(prophets) and like all who truly approve(believe) the talks of this book. Worship God only!\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 10\~}
And he told me, \u8220?Do not keep secretly the talks of the prophecy of this buk, because the time become near. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 11\~}
Let the one who does wrong continue to do wrong. Let the destroyed person continue to be destroyed. Let the one who does good continue to do good, and let the without.dust(holy) person continue to be without.dust(holy).\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 12\~}
"Watch out! I am coming not.far! My reward is with me, and I will give to each one according to what they have done. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 13\~}
I am the Alfa and the Omega, the First and the Last, the Beginning and the End.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 14\~}
Blessed are those who wash their clothes clean and they can eat the fruit from the tree of life and to go through the gates into the city. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 15\~}
But outside the city are dogs, those who practice sorcery, the immoral, the murderers, those who worship idols and every people who loves and practices false life.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 16\~}
"I, Yesu, have sent my man carrying heavenly message to announce these things to you.p in the Yesu's families(churches). I am the Descendant of Deifid, and bright Morning Star.\u8221?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 17\~}
The God Spirit and the bride say, \u8220?Come!\u8221? And let the one who hears say, \u8220?Come!\u8221? Let the one who is thirsty come, and let the one who wishes, take the water of life without payment.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 18\~}
I warn every people who hears the talks of the prophecy of this buk: If anyone adds in this buk, God will add to that person the fearful suffering things described in this buk. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 19\~}
And if anyone takes talks away from this buk of prophecy, God will take away their authority to eat the fruit of tree of life, and to enter the Without.dust City, which are told in this buk.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs28 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs28 20\~}
